title: Independent Muhammad Ghulam Sarwar wins PP-204 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Muhammad Ghulam Sarwar, an independent has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-204, Sahiwal VI by securing 60,438 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an independent candidate Adil Saeed Chaudhry, who bagged 33,722 votes.
Votersâ€™ turn- out remained 57.58 percent.
